com.yworks.yfiles.graph.styles

Class GeneralPathNodeStyle

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yworks.yfiles.graph.styles.GeneralPathNodeStyle
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    INodeStyle, ICloneable, Cloneable

    public class GeneralPathNodeStyle
extends Object
implements INodeStyle, Cloneable
    A node style that can display node shapes with a boundary that is defined by a GeneralPath instance.

      • getPath

        public GeneralPath getPath()
        Gets the path that defines the boundary of the shape.

        The path must be defined in such a way that <0,0> will be at the top left of a node's Layout and <1,1> will be at the lower right. The path will be scaled accordingly during the painting.

        The default is a simple rectangular path.

        Returns:
        The Path.
        See Also:
        setPath(GeneralPath)
